In a surprise move, Netflix has acquired the rights to the 2027 and
2031 Women=E2=80=99s World Cup, stunning the industry and amplifying expect=
ations about its live sports ambitions.

John Ourand ( https://puck.news/author/john-ourand/?utm_campaign=3DThe+Vars=
ity+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F23%2F24%29&utm_content=3DThe+Varsity+-+SUBSCRIBER=
